panci berisi air.  Dimana itu?

00:07:20.880 --> 00:07:22.800
W-Air.. Yah..

00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:26.120
Bibi, air.. Sebenarnya..

00:07:26.200 --> 00:07:28.400
Nenek..

